    <div class="card-title">3️⃣ Fonctions d'Agrégation</div>
    <div class="concept-grid">
      <div class="concept-card" style="--c:#6c63ff">
        <h4>COUNT(*)</h4>
        <p>Compte le nombre de lignes.</p>
        <code style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--accent3)">SELECT COUNT(*) FROM film;</code>
      </div>
      <div class="concept-card" style="--c:#ff6b9d">
        <h4>SUM(col)</h4>
        <p>Somme des valeurs d'une colonne.</p>
        <code style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--accent3)">SELECT SUM(amount) FROM payment;</code>
      </div>
      <div class="concept-card" style="--c:#ffa94d">
        <h4>AVG(col)</h4>
        <p>Moyenne des valeurs.</p>
        <code style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--accent3)">SELECT AVG(rental_rate) FROM film;</code>
      </div>
      <div class="concept-card" style="--c:#00d4aa">
        <h4>MAX / MIN</h4>
        <p>Valeur maximale ou minimale.</p>
        <code style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--accent3)">SELECT MAX(length) FROM film;</code>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- DISTINCT & GROUP BY -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">4️⃣ DISTINCT & GROUP BY</div>
    <div class="code-block">
      <div class="code-label">DISTINCT + GROUP BY</div>
<span class="cm">-- Types de notations uniques dans la BDD</span>
<span class="kw">SELECT DISTINCT</span> rating <span class="kw">FROM</span> film<span class="str">;</span>

<span class="cm">-- Nombre de films par notation (rating)</span>
<span class="kw">SELECT</span> rating, <span class="fn">COUNT</span>(*) <span class="kw">AS</span> nb_films
<span class="kw">FROM</span> film
<span class="kw">GROUP BY</span> rating
<span class="kw">ORDER BY</span> nb_films <span class="fn">DESC</span><span class="str">;</span>

<span class="cm">-- Total des paiements par client</span>
<span class="kw">SELECT</span> customer_id, <span class="fn">SUM</span>(amount) <span class="kw">AS</span> total
<span class="kw">FROM</span> payment
<span class="kw">GROUP BY</span> customer_id
<span class="kw">ORDER BY</span> total <span class="fn">DESC</span><span class="str">;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="callout callout-info">
      <span class="callout-icon">💡</span>
      <div>Règle : tout ce qui est dans le <strong>SELECT</strong> et qui n'est pas une fonction d'agrégation <strong>doit être dans le GROUP BY</strong>.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

