    <div class="exercise">
      <div class="exercise-label">✏️ Exercice 4 — LIKE & BETWEEN</div>
      <p>a) Trouve tous les acteurs dont le prénom (first_name) commence par "J".<br>
      b) Trouve les films dont le rental_rate est entre 1.00 et 3.00.</p>
      <details class="answer">
        <summary><span class="summary-arrow">▶</span> Voir la correction</summary>
        <div class="answer-content">
          <table class="ans-table" style="margin-bottom:0.8rem">
            <tr><th>Opérateur</th><th>Pattern utilisé</th><th>Signification</th></tr>
            <tr><td class="pk">LIKE 'J%'</td><td class="attr">'J%'</td><td class="attr">Commence par J, suivi de n'importe quoi</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="pk">BETWEEN 1.00 AND 3.00</td><td class="attr">1.00 ≤ x ≤ 3.00</td><td class="attr">Bornes incluses</td></tr>
          </table>
          <div class="ans-code"><span class="c-cm">-- a) Prénoms commençant par J</span>
<span class="c-kw">SELECT</span> first_name, last_name
<span class="c-kw">FROM</span> actor
<span class="c-kw">WHERE</span> first_name <span class="c-fn">LIKE</span> <span class="c-str">'J%'</span>;

<span class="c-cm">-- b) Rental rate entre 1.00 et 3.00</span>
<span class="c-kw">SELECT</span> title, rental_rate
<span class="c-kw">FROM</span> film
<span class="c-kw">WHERE</span> rental_rate <span class="c-fn">BETWEEN</span> <span class="c-num">1.00</span> <span class="c-fn">AND</span> <span class="c-num">3.00</span>;</div>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="exercise">
